					<description><![CDATA[<p>Send newsletters that stand out from the crowd with these expert tips and tricks.</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/how-to-write-a-newsletter">7 Steps to Write a Newsletter (With or Without AI!)</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.wordstream.com">WordStream</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The opaque algorithms of social media and search engines make email still one of the best ways to reach your target audience. But here‚Äôs the catch: everyone‚Äôs inbox is crowded nowadays, so you must elbow your way for attention.</p>
<p>To help you understand the art and science behind a successful newsletter, we‚Äôre dissecting the key elements and sharing best practices and examples from attention-grabbing newsletters.</p>
<p>Ready to give your newsletter a fresh coat of paint? Let‚Äôs start.</p>
