<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/holiday-email-templates-seasons-greetings.png" alt="holiday email templates to customers - seasons greetings red theme" width="468" height="608" class=" wp-image-67979 aligncenter" /></p>
<h3>Template #6: Christmas sale promotion</h3>
<blockquote><p>Hey [Name],</p>
<p>Santa&#8217;s elves ain&#8217;t got nothin&#8217; on us! We&#8217;re cranking out deals faster than you can say &#8220;Merry Christmas!&#8221;</p>
<p>Our Christmas sale is in full swing, and it&#8217;s BIGGER and BETTER than ever! From snug sweaters and stylish jackets to chic dresses and trendy accessories, there&#8217;s something for everyone on your list.</p>
<p>The icing on the gingerbread? Enjoy discounts of up to 40% off on our entire Christmas collection. Bot don&#8217;t dilly-dally; this offer won&#8217;t last forever! Santa&#8217;s reindeer are tapping their hooves, and we woudn&#8217;t want you to miss the best deals of the season.</p>
<p>Click here to sleigh thorugh the sale. Wishing you a holly, jolly holiday season!</p>
<p>P.S Explore our special gifts section for stocking stuffers and unique presents guaranteed to bring smiles.</p></blockquote>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Holiday-email-templates-wordstream-christmas-sale.webp" alt="Holiday email templates - screenshot of a holiday sale email." width="455" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-87407 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Holiday-email-templates-wordstream-christmas-sale.webp 455w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Holiday-email-templates-wordstream-christmas-sale-228x300.webp 228w" sizes="(max-width: 455px) 100vw, 455px" /></p>
