<p>Without your enthusiasm and energy, we wouldn‚Äôt be where we are now.</p>
<p>Thanks to your feedback, we added eight¬†new features to ProductName this year and earned our highest rating on ReviewPlatform yet. And because of your referrals, we helped twice as many small businesses get online this year than last.¬†And because of you, we love our jobs!</p>
<p>Not only are we excited for 2022 with you, but we also have some big goals and big ideas that we can‚Äôt wait to share. So stay tuned! But for now, enjoy the holiday season!</p>
<p>With many thanks,</p>
<p>The ProductName¬†Team</p></blockquote>
